1
00:02:06,345 --> 00:02:08,024
Stay by my side…

2
00:02:10,985 --> 00:02:12,545
and don't go anywhere.

3
00:02:14,385 --> 00:02:15,904
Your mom said,

4
00:02:17,344 --> 00:02:19,344
love isn't about doing
something for someone.

5
00:02:20,904 --> 00:02:23,145
It's about putting your heart into it.

6
00:02:23,624 --> 00:02:27,305
How are you involved with what happened
to Nut and his mother?

7
00:02:27,385 --> 00:02:30,745
You're nosy because you're jealous
of Nut's mother, right?

8
00:02:31,985 --> 00:02:33,425
Why would I be jealous?

9
00:02:33,505 --> 00:02:35,785
Well, everybody loves her.

10
00:02:36,505 --> 00:02:37,785
This includes Mr. Saen too.

11
00:02:39,945 --> 00:02:41,825
Have you heard of the phrase

12
00:02:41,904 --> 00:02:45,305
"Pity is the foundation of love"?

13
00:02:46,745 --> 00:02:49,665
No. I've only heard of sympathy.

14
00:03:07,105 --> 00:03:08,145
I'm off, Mom.

15
00:03:10,585 --> 00:03:11,545
Tofu.

16
00:03:12,184 --> 00:03:13,784
Want to see the series you were in?

17
00:03:14,265 --> 00:03:16,624
Juea just finished editing the teaser.

18
00:03:16,705 --> 00:03:17,585
Do you?

19
00:03:20,225 --> 00:03:21,585
I shouldn't.

20
00:03:22,585 --> 00:03:24,825
I just went out yesterday.

21
00:03:24,904 --> 00:03:28,025
I was going to help your mom
with the chores.

22
00:03:29,545 --> 00:03:31,504
Don't worry about me.

23
00:03:32,184 --> 00:03:34,385
I'm healthy now.
I can take care of myself.

24
00:03:34,865 --> 00:03:37,265
You should do what you want,
so you don't get bored.

25
00:03:40,025 --> 00:03:41,585
Maybe another time.

26
00:03:42,265 --> 00:03:44,464
I have a lot to do.

27
00:03:45,265 --> 00:03:47,464
That's up to you. I'm off.

28
00:03:49,784 --> 00:03:50,665
Bye.

29
00:03:52,504 --> 00:03:53,585
Bye, Keunchai.

30
00:04:03,624 --> 00:04:04,745
Song.

31
00:04:12,385 --> 00:04:14,105
Oh, Tofu. What is it?

32
00:04:15,265 --> 00:04:17,824
Song. Can you do me a favor?

33
00:04:26,665 --> 00:04:28,185
Do you know

34
00:04:28,824 --> 00:04:33,225
which close friend of Neung
has a name that begins with "T".

35
00:04:34,945 --> 00:04:36,065
Is it Thanayut,

36
00:04:37,385 --> 00:04:38,584
Title,

37
00:04:39,745 --> 00:04:40,745
or Tatarn?

38
00:04:42,385 --> 00:04:44,945
Neung's close friend
with a name beginning with a "T"…

39
00:04:46,144 --> 00:04:47,584
I think he's the only one.

40
00:04:48,945 --> 00:04:50,065
Tatarn.

41
00:04:53,505 --> 00:04:55,745
That one. They have a picture together.

42
00:04:58,345 --> 00:04:59,264
This one?

43
00:05:00,505 --> 00:05:01,465
That's right.

44
00:05:09,065 --> 00:05:12,305
Watch this. I just finished editing.

45
00:05:14,264 --> 00:05:15,345
There.

