47
00:06:31,945 --> 00:06:35,185
There's only one moon.

48
00:06:40,144 --> 00:06:41,985
How about I draw another moon?

49
00:06:47,065 --> 00:06:48,584
If you draw another moon,

50
00:06:49,144 --> 00:06:51,185
the first moon will lose its meaning.

51
00:06:59,425 --> 00:07:00,824
